This paper deals with image labeling, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of graphical models and message passing algorithms is also a common approach in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of geometric assignment, which is related to computational geometry (cs.CG) and graph theory (cs.DS). Finally, the paper deals with optimization problems, which is a common theme in operations research (cs.GR).
